  "text": "9. Enforced disintegration. This was based on stimuli used by [CITATION_1] . The stimulus resembles a launching stimulus, except that, when object A contacts object B, object B disintegrates into 9 small rectangles that disperse in various directions, though with a rightward tendency. To maintain consistency with the other stimuli for this experiment, object A was a black rectangle instead of the black disc used by [CITATION_2] .",
